msgid "Advanced AI technology to fight misinformation"
msgstr "Dezinformatsiyaga qarshi kurashish uchun ilg'or AI texnologiyasi"

msgid "1. Paste the News"
msgstr "1. Yangilikni joylashtiring"

msgid "Copy any news article, social media post, or suspicious text and paste it into our analyzer."
msgstr "Istalgan yangilik maqolasi, ijtimoiy tarmoq yozuvi yoki shubhali matnni nusxalab, tahlilchimizga joylashtiring."

msgid "2. AI Analysis"
msgstr "2. AI tahlili"

msgid "Our DeepSeek AI model analyzes language patterns, logical consistency, and known misinformation signals."
msgstr "Bizning DeepSeek AI modelimiz til naqshlarini, mantiqiy izchillikni va ma'lum dezinformatsiya belgilarini tahlil qiladi."

msgid "3. Get Results"
msgstr "3. Natijalarni oling"

msgid "Receive a clear verdict (Real / Fake / Uncertain) with a confidence score and detailed reasoning."
msgstr "Ishonch ko'rsatkichi va batafsil asoslar bilan aniq hukm oling (Haqiqiy / Soxta / Noaniq)."

msgid "Ready to Fight Misinformation?"
msgstr "Dezinformatsiyaga qarshi kurashishga tayyormisiz?"

msgid "Create a free account and start detecting fake news with the power of AI."
msgstr "Bepul hisob yarating va AI kuchi bilan soxta yangiliklar aniqlashni boshlang."

msgid "Start For Free"
msgstr "Bepul boshlash"

msgid "About FakeNews AI"
msgstr "FakeNews AI haqida"

msgid "An AI-powered system designed to help people identify misinformation and fake news in the digital age."
msgstr "Raqamli asrda odamlarga dezinformatsiya va soxta yangiliklar aniqlashga yordam berish uchun yaratilgan AI tizimi."

msgid "Our Mission"
msgstr "Bizning vazifamiz"

msgid "We believe accurate information is the foundation of a healthy society. Our mission is to make AI-powered fact-checking accessible to everyone, helping people make informed decisions about the news they consume and share."
msgstr "Biz to'g'ri ma'lumot sog'lom jamiyatning asosi deb hisoblaymiz. Bizning vazifamiz AI asosidagi fakt tekshirishni hamma uchun ochiq qilish."

msgid "Technology"
msgstr "Texnologiya"

msgid "Built on DeepSeek AI via OpenRouter, our system analyzes linguistic patterns, logical consistency, emotional manipulation tactics, and structural markers commonly found in fake news to provide accurate verdicts."
msgstr "OpenRouter orqali DeepSeek AI asosida qurilgan tizimimiz til naqshlari, mantiqiy izchillik va hissiy manipulyatsiya taktikalarini tahlil qiladi."

msgid "3 Languages"
msgstr "3 til"

msgid "English, Russian, and Uzbek support for wider accessibility."
msgstr "Keng qamrovlilik uchun ingliz, rus va o'zbek tillarini qo'llab-quvvatlash."

msgid "Fast Analysis"
msgstr "Tezkor tahlil"

msgid "Results in seconds using state-of-the-art language models."
msgstr "Zamonaviy til modellari yordamida soniyalar ichida natijalar."

msgid "Analysis History"
msgstr "Tahlil tarixi"

msgid "All your analyses are saved for future reference."
msgstr "Barcha tahlillaringiz keyingi foydalanish uchun saqlanadi."

msgid "Disclaimer"
msgstr "Mas'uliyatsizlik"

msgid "FakeNews AI is a tool to assist in evaluating news content. AI analysis should be used as a starting point for critical thinking, not as a definitive fact-checker. Always verify information through multiple credible sources."
msgstr "FakeNews AI yangilik mazmunini baholashga yordam beruvchi vositadir. AI tahlili tanqidiy fikrlash uchun boshlang'ich nuqta sifatida ishlatilishi kerak. Ma'lumotlarni har doim bir nechta ishonchli manbalar orqali tasdiqlang."

